## 🛠️ Troubleshooting

### Error: "mkcert: comando no encontrado"
```powershell
choco install mkcert
```

### Error: "Port 8000 already in use"
```powershell
netstat -ano | findstr :8000
taskkill /PID <PID> /F
```

### Error: "Certificados no confían"
Ver: [MKCERT_TLS_1.3_GUIA.md](MKCERT_TLS_1.3_GUIA.md) → Troubleshooting

